KDE INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
------------------------

sudo pacman --noconfirm -Syu base-devel binutils yay bash-completion kitty rofi vifm gcc-libs poetry flameshot
sudo pacman --noconfirm -Rs yakuake okular konversation kate kcalc spectacle manjaro-hello

Change Caps lock to control.

Import control scheme into shortcuts

Go to Settings -> Workspace -> Window Management -> Window rules -> regex .* and no titlebar with Force option.
      Settings -> Workspace -> Workspace Behavior -> General Behavior -> Animation Speed = Instant

Change theme to Breeze.

Change desktop background.

Delete Desktop folder and change desktop settings so that there is no desktop folder.


Before running the nix install script. Run 
rm .bashrc .bash_profile .config/kwinrulesrc .config/kwinrc .dir_colors
